This project falls under the scope of GNOME's Code of Conduct, which can be found here: 
https://wiki.gnome.org/Foundation/CodeOfConduct

----

If you have concerns someone has violated the Code of Conduct, please contact GNOME's Code of Conduct Committee. Even if you are unsure
an incident is covered by the Code of Conduct, you are encouraged to report it.

A report can be made by emailing code-of-conduct-committee@gnome.org

Detailed information regarding reporting, including what information in include, can be found here:
https://wiki.gnome.org/Foundation/CodeOfConduct/ReporterGuide